domain

Class Paddle

  • java.lang.Object
    • domain.GameObject
      • domain.Paddle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Paddle
extends GameObject
    OVERVIEW: This class is used for the most essential component of the game. Paddle has 6 values; centerX and centerY is for calculating the rotation and x1,x2,y1,y2 are the corner coordinate values of the paddle. Boolean rotateLeft, and rotateRight are for turning the rotation on or off.
    Author:
    The Hackermen Team
